### Hotel Acquamarina API - Ejemplos de Peticiones HTTP
### Puedes usar este archivo con las extensiones REST Client de VSCode o similar

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = tu_token_aqui

### ===========================================
### AUTENTICACIÓN
### ===========================================

### Registro de nuevo usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Usuario Prueba",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Registro de Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@acquamarina.com",
  "password": "Admin123!",
  "fullName": "Administrador Hotel",
  "phone": "+123456789",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Obtener perfil del usuario autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### HABITACIONES
### ===========================================

### Listar todas las habitaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms

###

### Crear habitación simple
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNumber": "101",
  "type": "single",
  "pricePerNight": 80,
  "capacity": 1,
  "maxChildren": 0,
  "description": "Habitación individual con vista al jardín",
  "amenities": ["WiFi", "TV", "Aire acondicionado"],
  "status": "available"
}

###

### Crear habitación doble
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNumber": "201",
  "type": "double",
  "pricePerNight": 120,
  "capacity": 2,
  "maxChildren": 1,
  "description": "Habitación doble con vista al mar",
  "amenities": ["WiFi", "TV", "Aire acondicionado", "Mini bar", "Balcón"],
  "status": "available"
}

###

### Crear suite
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNumber": "301",
  "type": "suite",
  "pricePerNight": 250,
  "capacity": 2,
  "maxChildren": 2,
  "description": "Suite de lujo con jacuzzi y vista panorámica",
  "amenities": ["WiFi", "TV", "Aire acondicionado", "Mini bar", "Jacuzzi", "Balcón", "Sala de estar"],
  "status": "available"
}

###

### Crear habitación familiar
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNumber": "401",
  "type": "family",
  "pricePerNight": 180,
  "capacity": 4,
  "maxChildren": 3,
  "description": "Habitación amplia ideal para familias",
  "amenities": ["WiFi", "TV", "Aire acondicionado", "Cocina pequeña", "2 baños"],
  "status": "available"
}

###

### Obtener habitación por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/ID_HABITACION_AQUI

###

### Buscar habitaciones disponibles
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/available?checkIn=2025-02-01&checkOut=2025-02-05

###

### Actualizar habitación
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rooms/ID_HABITACION_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pricePerNight": 175,
  "status": "available"
}

###

### Eliminar habitación
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rooms/ID_HABITACION_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### RESERVAS
### ===========================================

### Crear reserva
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2025-02-15",
  "checkOutDate": "2025-02-20",
  "numberOfAdults": 2,
  "numberOfChildren": 1,
  "guestName": "María González",
  "guestEmail": "maria@example.com",
  "guestPhone": "+123456789",
  "specialRequests": "Cama extra para niño, vista al mar preferentemente",
  "roomId": "ID_HABITACION_AQUI"
}

###

### Listar todas las reservas (Admin) o mis reservas (Usuario)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mis reservas (Usuario autenticado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/my-reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener reserva por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_RESERVA_AQUI

###

### Actualizar reserva
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_RESERVA_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "specialRequests": "Solicitud actualizada: llegada tarde después de las 10pm",
  "numberOfChildren": 2
}

###

### Confirmar reserva
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_RESERVA_AQUI/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Cancelar reserva
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_RESERVA_AQUI/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eliminar reserva
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reservations/ID_RESERVA_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### USUARIOS (requiere autenticación)
### ===========================================

### Listar todos los usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener usuario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/ID_USUARIO_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nuevo@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Nuevo Usuario",
  "phone": "+9876543210",
  "role": "user"
}

###

### Actualizar usuario
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/ID_USUARIO_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Nombre Actualizado",
  "phone": "+1111111111"
}

###

### Eliminar usuario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/ID_USUARIO_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
